Properties.Description:
Light tactical vehicle offering high speed and versatility, optimized for efficient short-ranged transport. Ideal for scouting runs and rapid deployment across varied terrain. However, its emphasis on speed comes at the expense of protection--avoid direct combat whenever possible.

The only known origin is the S9-WARDEN. However, the intended purpose is unknown. There has been no reported observations of it ever being used by any robot. What is their plan, and what are they doing in that Vault?
This vehicle will decay while the engine is running.
